    <h1>About the Developer</h1>
    <p class="rz-static-lead">Meet the mind behind Rizzzler – a passion project built for creators.</p>

    <div class="rz-about-grid">
      <div class="rz-about-text">
        <p>Rizzzler was born from a simple idea: <strong>one link to rule them all</strong>. I wanted a space where anyone could build a beautiful, personal showcase page in seconds – without coding, without complexity.</p>
        <p>As a developer, I’m obsessed with clean design, smooth animations, and making technology accessible. Rizzzler reflects that: themes, music, gallery, and custom links, all wrapped in a lightweight package that loads fast and looks stunning.</p>
        <p>This is a solo project built with ❤️ and a lot of coffee. Every feature you see comes from a genuine desire to help people express themselves online.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rz-about-stats">
        <div class="rz-about-stat">
          <span class="rz-about-stat-number">1</span>
          <span class="rz-about-stat-label">Developer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rz-about-stat">
          <span class="rz-about-stat-number">∞</span>
          <span class="rz-about-stat-label">Ideas</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rz-about-stat">
