    <div class="rz-static-section">
      <h2>Contribute &amp; Connect</h2>
      <p>If you have suggestions, bug reports, or just want to say hi, reach out at <a href="mailto:developerpuneet2010@gmail.com">developerpuneet2010@gmail.com</a>. Feedback is always welcome!</p>
